00:17:59,812 --> 00:18:02,214
"How to Change the World"
by David Bornstein...

00:18:02,214 --> 00:18:03,516
Mm.

00:18:03,516 --> 00:18:05,418
...In which he talks about
social entrepreneurship

00:18:05,418 --> 00:18:06,586
in third-world countries

00:18:06,586 --> 00:18:08,487
and how that's really
making a difference.

00:18:08,487 --> 00:18:10,590
Jason, I just read
