00:18:40,786 --> 00:18:42,321
Thank you.

00:18:42,321 --> 00:18:44,991
Look, when I was 16,
I wasn't doing electronics,

00:18:44,991 --> 00:18:47,126
but I was buying
and selling stamps.

00:18:47,126 --> 00:18:48,694
I already knew
what I could sell it for...

00:18:48,694 --> 00:18:50,429
Mm-hmm.
...So I could flip it
very quickly.

00:18:50,429 --> 00:18:51,530
Exactly what this is.

00:18:51,530 --> 00:18:53,432
That's exactly
what this is.
Right.

00:18:53,432 --> 00:18:55,801
